dataprimeQuery.text: source logs | filter ($p.Application == null || $l.applicationname.inArray($p.Application)) | filter $m.severity == INFO | groupby $m.timestamp / $p.timeRange.suggestedInterval as timestamp agg count() as count
source spans | groupby $m.timestamp / $p.timeRange.suggestedInterval as timestamp agg count() as count
source logs | groupby $l.subsystemname agg count() as count
source logs | groupby $l.subsystemname agg count() as count
source spans | filter tags['http.route'] != null | countby tags['http.route']
source logs | groupby $l.applicationname, $l.subsystemname agg count() as count
source spans | filter $d.tags['http.method'] != null | groupby $l.subsystemName, $d.tags['http.method'] agg count() as count
source logs | groupby $l.subsystemname as subsystem agg count() as count
